data.description: A true sanctuary in the heart of Oak Terrace. Welcome to 829 Redwood Ave, a captivating residence on a spacious double lot, boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an attached garage, and a refreshing inground pool. At 1,641 SqFt, this home welcomes you with an inviting open floor plan and thoughtfully designed split bedrooms for added privacy and comfort. The heart of the home lies in the kitchen, adorned with a generous granite countertop, perfect for casual dining and morning gatherings. Seamlessly connected to the living room, it creates an ideal space for effortless entertainment and relaxation. Indulge in leisurely afternoons by the poolside, soaking in the sun's rays, and unwinding amidst the tranquility of majestic oak trees. This residence has been meticulously enhanced with modern upgrades, including a new AC system, laminate flooring, recessed lighting, a new sand filter for the pool, crown molding, and updated risers in the septic system. Offering $5,000.00 in concessions
